## File Output

Log files are written to the parent directory of `LOG_FILE_PATH`. Example
output for two turns in one session:

```
"timestamp","chat_id","user_id","user_name","module","part_no","user_message","assistant_response"
"2026-04-30T14:30:22.123456+00:00","abc12345xyz","user_001","J. Smith","WING_SPAR","12345-001","Crack near fastener row B, ~0.5 inches. What have we seen?","Based on retrieved DR history, DR-00412 describes a similar crack..."
"2026-04-30T14:31:05.654321+00:00","abc12345xyz","user_001","J. Smith","WING_SPAR","12345-001","What was the resolution on DR-00412?","DR-00412 was dispositioned via rework — the affected area was..."
```

